<%= section "Overview of topics" do %>

The topics section is where you add and organize course materials in OST. Your course material will be sorted into topics As the chart explains, OST builds assignments by pulling content from topics. 

<center>
<%= image_tag("topics_chart.png", {:border => 1, :width => "70%", :height => "70%", :title=>"create new topic"})%>
</center>

A topic is 
(a) a group of related exercises and resources; <br/>
(b) a building block of the assignments you will create in OST. </br>

<p>How you organize your topics is up to you.</p> 

<% end %>

